items.title: Hundreds of soldiers on standby for possible deployment to Minneapolis amid protests
items.description: About 1,500 active-duty soldiers are on standby in Alaska for possible deployment to Minneapolis, a U.S. defense official told CBS News Saturday.

items.title: Shark mauls surfer in Sydney day after boy bitten, critically injured
items.description: A surfer was attacked one day after a large shark bit a 12-year-old boy in the legs, leaving him fighting for survival in a hospital.

items.title: What's open and closed on Martin Luther King Jr. Day 2026?
items.description: Most stores on Monday are open during their regular business hours on Martin Luther King Jr. Day, with a few exceptions.
